Wednesday, October 18, 2000

MERIT DOCKET

00-1424. State ex rel. Harman v. Cacioppo.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss and/or motion for summary judgment. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
